=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"a8f3ffbc265a364dfac3fb4d51a7130b12aa958a","tid":1640692,"uid":171273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/36iketnovdr31.jpg?width=960&amp;crop=smart&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=83eabeae9f2a97aac7767fb0447c3a02af3c43f4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2F36iketnovdr31.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960%26crop%3Dsmart%26auto%3Dwebp%26s%3D83eabeae9f2a97aac7767fb0447c3a02af3c43f4&h=0dfb4332&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcb9e4a76f3fe52c8f4c9aa4a1ec605f5a0d976f","tid":1640692,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794a833337bc2cbcf6cdd8a6848878ca3d8148ae","tid":1640692,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8253